{"tid":1833063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警犬FB工作報告【打擊違例泊車 確保道路暢通】","createTime":"2020-01-21T15:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T15:21:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccbd8661d8d3a060b2d22e8cb1c9b703b5659e7c","tid":1833063,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"【打擊違例泊車 確保道路暢通】<br />\n<br />\n為確保道路暢通，警方近日在港九新界各區的違例泊車黑點，重點執法，打擊違例停泊。<br />\n<br />\n違例停泊除了影響其他道路使用者外，更有可能導致交通意外。警方呼籲駕駛人士，切勿因一時之便，違例停泊車輛。<br />\n<br />\nTo ensure smooth traffic, the Police have recently stepped up traffic enforcement actions against illegal parking in different traffic black spots across Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nIllegal parking not only brings inconvenience to road users, but may even lead to traffic accidents. The Police appeal to all drivers to refrain from illegal parking for personal conveniences.<br />\n<br />\n#HKPpolicing<br />\n#路上零意外<br />\n#香港人人愛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/2919012418186703/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F960526577368640%2Fposts%2F2919012418186703%2F&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=83cf074d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/960526577368640/posts/2919012418186703/</a>"},{"pid":"e0a5596b46811f39367702d005a9a488df969e01","tid":1833063,"uid":5929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"本身就係份內事 <br />\n做野講出黎要比人讚<br />\n要比骨頭你獎你啊？"},{"pid":"d5669773c067a6d58a5f7098c49416aadbd0d287","tid":1833063,"uid":277261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e0a5596b46811f39367702d005a9a488df969e01","tid":1833063,"uid":5929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"本身就係份內事 <br />\n做野講出黎要比人讚<br />\n要比骨頭你獎你啊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"係想合理化前兩日隔眼拉個人落車拘捕佢果單違法泊車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"